    "TRY THE HEW Victory Cafe Opposite Orpheum Theatre Henry Kittelson Owner Lloyd Smith Manager WASHINGTON FISH AND OYSTER CO P1RT WILLIAMS ALUKA Cold Storage Frozen Bait Ice Total freezing capacity 20 tons daily KODIAK DIARY The lone gentleman who late at night on Monday was snoop ing around a house on Knudsea apartment hill and ran off into the brush when the man of the house came out to investigate may be interested in knowing that as his darkened figure ran into the brush a shot was fired at him He should be thankful too that in his hurry the man of the house grabbed the one of his two guns which was not loaded He reports that he has them both loaded now Cappy Brodtkorb who does not like to have his name mis spelled with a p on the end of it submits the following as his favorite story In a Kentucky court a negro was arraigned for trial on a charge of mayhem As Exhibit A for the case the mutilated vic tim of his wrath was presented a lamentable spectacle before the eyes of judge and jury Now the face of the victim was but little"
